lower prices for international telephone calls on Hongkong
Telecommunications' earnings were incorrect. The words 'optimistic' and
'pessimistic' were transposed during compilation.
In addition, Hongkong Telecom's international revenues in 1992 were
HKDollars 11,084m. The corrected table will be published in Monday's
edition.
